high_descs: Turn left and go toward the shower, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
Go to the cabinet beneath the sink, to the left of the toilet.
Open the cabinet, put the bar of soap inside, and close the cabinet.
Turn left and move forward, then turn right to face the counter between the sink basins.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Return to the cabinet to the left of the toilet.
Open the cabinet, put the bar of soap inside, and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the toilet tank
Pick up the soap on the tank
Turn around adjust your position and look at the sink cabinet
Open the cabinet and put in the soap then close the cabinet
Turn left head to the sink counter
Pick up the soap on the counter
Turn right then adjust your position and look at the sink cabinet
Open the cabinet and put in the soap then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put two soap in the cabinet

high_descs: Make a left to reach the sink across the room.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink countertop, the one farthest to the right.
Turn to face the cabinet under the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the rightmost cabinet under the sink.
Walk to the left-hand sink.
Pick up the bar of soap sitting in between the two sinks.
Turn to face the cabinet under the right sink.
Put the other bar of soap in the rightmost cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in a cabinet under the sink.
